          <h2 class="text-3xl font-serif font-bold text-white mb-4" style="letter-spacing:-0.02em;">Chcesz sprzedać mieszkanie szybko?</h2>
          <p class="text-white/70 mb-8 max-w-md mx-auto" style="line-height:1.75;">Skontaktuj się z nami – wycenimy Twoją nieruchomość bezpłatnie i bez zobowiązań w ciągu 24 godzin.</p>
          <a href="/#kontakt" class="btn-primary inline-block text-white px-10 py-4 rounded-xl font-semibold text-base" style="box-shadow:0 8px 24px rgba(166,122,68,0.35);">Uzyskaj bezpłatną wycenę</a>
        </div>
      </article>

      <!-- STICKY SIDEBAR -->
      <aside class="hidden lg:block" style="align-self: start; position: sticky; top: 88px; width: 340px;">
        <div id="article-sidebar">
          <div class="shadow-sidebar rounded-2xl overflow-hidden">
            <div style="height:4px; background:linear-gradient(90deg,#A67A44,#B8914F);"></div>
            <div style="background:linear-gradient(160deg,#1D3033 0%,#243B41 100%); padding:28px;">
              <div style="display:flex; align-items:center; gap:14px; margin-bottom:20px;">
                <div style="width:48px; height:48px; border-radius:50%; background:linear-gradient(135deg,#A67A44,#B8914F); display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; font-family:'Playfair Display',Georgia,serif; font-size:20px; font-weight:700; color:white; flex-shrink:0;">P</div>
                <div>
                  <p style="color:white; font-weight:600; font-size:15px; margin:0 0 2px;">Piotrek</p>
                  <p style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.42); font-size:12px; margin:0;">Specjalista ds. skupu nieruchomości</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <h3 style="font-family:'Playfair Display',Georgia,serif; color:white; font-size:1.2rem; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:-0.01em; margin:0 0 7px;">Darmowa wycena</h3>
              <p style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.52); font-size:13.5px; line-height:1.65; margin:0 0 20px;">Skontaktuj się ze mną – odpiszę w&nbsp;ciągu 24&nbsp;godzin.</p>
              <a href="tel:+48739503924" id="sidebar-phone" style="display:flex; align-items:center; gap:12px; margin-bottom:20px; text-decoration:none;">
                <div style="width:40px; height:40px; border-radius:12px; background:rgba(166,122,68,0.18); display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; flex-shrink:0;">
                  <svg width="18" height="18" fill="none" stroke="#A67A44" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 6V5z"/></svg>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <p style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.42); font-size:11px; margin:0 0 2px; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:0.06em;">Zadzwoń teraz</p>
                  <p class="sidebar-phone-num" style="color:white; font-weight:600; font-size:15px; margin:0; transition:color 0.2s;">+48 739 503 924</p>
                </div>
              </a>
              <div style="height:1px; background:rgba(255,255,255,0.1); margin-bottom:20px;"></div>
              <form id="sidebar-form">
                <div style="margin-bottom:10px;">
                  <input type="text" name="imie" placeholder="Imię" required class="sidebar-input"
                    style="display:block; width:100%; padding:11px 14px; border-radius:10px; background:rgba(255,255,255,0.07); border:1.5px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12); color:white; font-size:13.5px; font-family:'Inter',sans-serif; transition:border-color 0.2s;" />
                </div>
                <div style="margin-bottom:10px;">
                  <input type="tel" name="telefon" placeholder="Numer telefonu" required class="sidebar-input"
                    style="display:block; width:100%; padding:11px 14px; border-radius:10px; background:rgba(255,255,255,0.07); border:1.5px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12); color:white; font-size:13.5px; font-family:'Inter',sans-serif; transition:border-color 0.2s;" />
                </div>
                <div style="margin-bottom:14px;">
                  <label style="display:flex; align-items:flex-start; gap:10px; cursor:pointer;">
                    <span style="position:relative; margin-top:2px; flex-shrink:0; width:18px; height:18px;">
                      <input type="checkbox" name="zgoda" required id="sidebar-consent"
                        style="position:absolute; opacity:0; width:0; height:0;" />
                      <span id="sidebar-consent-box" style="display:block; width:18px; height:18px; border-radius:5px; border:1.5px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.3); background:rgba(255,255,255,0.07); transition:background 0.15s, border-color 0.15s;"></span>
                      <svg id="sidebar-consent-check" style="position:absolute; inset:0; width:18px; height:18px; pointer-events:none; display:none;" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none">
                        <path d="M5 10l3.5 3.5L15 7" stroke="white" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                      </svg>
                    </span>
                    <span style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.48); font-size:11.5px; line-height:1.6; font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;">
                      <span style="color:#f87171;">*</span> Zapoznałem/-am się z <a href="/privacy.html" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.65); text-decoration:underline;">Polityką Prywatności</a> i wyrażam zgodę na przetwarzanie moich danych osobowych.
                    </span>
                  </label>
                  <p id="sidebar-consent-error" style="display:none; color:#f87171; font-size:11px; margin-top:4px; margin-left:28px; font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;">Ta zgoda jest wymagana.</p>
                </div>
                <button type="submit" id="sidebar-btn"
                  style="display:block; width:100%; padding:13px; border-radius:10px; background:linear-gradient(135deg,#A67A44,#B8914F); color:white; font-weight:600; font-size:14px; font-family:'Inter',sans-serif; cursor:pointer; border:none;">
                  Wyślij zapytanie →
                </button>
                <p id="sidebar-success" style="display:none; text-align:center; color:#6ee7b7; font-size:13px; margin-top:10px; font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;">✓ Dziękujemy! Odezwiemy się wkrótce.</p>
              </form>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </aside>

    </div><!-- /flex -->
  </div><!-- /max-w-6xl -->

  {otherPosts.length > 0 && (
    <section class="pb-24 border-t border-gray-100">
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 pt-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-serif font-bold text-brand-dark mb-10" style="letter-spacing:-0.02em;">Inne artykuły</h2>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
          {otherPosts.map((p) => {
            const bg = p.data.category === 'Poradnik' || p.data.category === 'Porównanie' || p.data.category === 'Rynek' ? '#A67A44' : '#1D3033';
            const d = p.data.pubDate.toLocaleDateString('pl-PL', { day: 'numeric', month: 'long', year: 'numeric' });
            return (
              <a href={`/artykuly/${p.id}`} class="card-article block rounded-2xl overflow-hidden border border-gray-100 shadow-card">
                <div class="relative overflow-hidden h-48">
                  <img src={p.data.heroImage} alt={p.data.title} title={p.data.title} class="card-img w-full h-full object-cover" />
                  <div class="absolute inset-0" style="background:linear-gradient(to top,rgba(29,48,51,0.5) 0%,transparent 60%);"></div>
                  <span class="absolute top-3 left-3 text-white text-xs font-semibold px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full" style={`background:${bg}`}>{p.data.category}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="p-6">
                  <p class="text-gray-400 text-xs mb-2">{d} · {p.data.readTime}</p>
                  <h3 class="font-serif font-bold text-brand-dark text-lg mb-2">{p.data.title}</h3>
                  <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-brand-orange font-semibold text-sm">Czytaj więcej <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"/></svg></span>
                </div>
              </a>
            );
          })}
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  )}

  <script is:inline>
    (function() {
      var FORMSPREE = 'https://formspree.io/f/xvzvrkrp';
      var form = document.getElementById('sidebar-form');
      if (!form) return;
      form.addEventListener('submit', async function(e) {
        e.preventDefault();
        var btn = document.getElementById('sidebar-btn');
        var nameVal  = form.querySelector('[name="imie"]').value.trim();
        var phoneVal = form.querySelector('[name="telefon"]').value.trim();
        var msgVal   = form.querySelector('[name="wiadomosc"]').value;
        var consentEl = form.querySelector('[name="zgoda"]');
        var consentOk = consentEl && consentEl.checked;
        var consentErr = document.getElementById('sidebar-consent-error');
        if (consentErr) consentErr.style.display = consentOk ? 'none' : 'block';
        if (!nameVal || !phoneVal || !consentOk) return;
        btn.textContent = 'Wysyłanie...';
        btn.disabled = true;
        try {
          var res = await fetch(FORMSPREE, {
            method: 'POST',
            headers: { 'Accept': 'application/json', 'Content-Type': 'application/json' },
            body: JSON.stringify({ imie: nameVal, telefon: phoneVal, wiadomosc: msgVal })
          });
          if (res.ok) {
            form.reset();
            document.getElementById('sidebar-success').style.display = 'block';
          } else {
            btn.textContent = 'Błąd – spróbuj ponownie';
            btn.disabled = false;
          }
        } catch(err) {
          btn.textContent = 'Błąd – spróbuj ponownie';
          btn.disabled = false;
        }
      });
    })();
  </script>

  <footer class="py-12 border-t border-white/10" style="background:#1D3033;">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-6">
        <span style="font-family:'Erode',serif;font-size:30px;font-weight:600;color:white;letter-spacing:0.01em;">SKUP NIERUCHOMOŚCI</span>
        <p class="text-white/40 text-sm text-center">© 2026 Skup Nieruchomości Łódź. Wszelkie prawa zastrzeżone.</p>
        <nav class="flex gap-6 text-sm text-white/60">
          <a href="/#o-nas" class="hover:text-brand-orange transition-colors">O nas</a>
          <a href="/#uslugi" class="hover:text-brand-orange transition-colors">Usługi</a>
          <a href="/#kontakt" class="hover:text-brand-orange transition-colors">Kontakt</a>
        </nav>
      </div>
    </div>
  </footer>

  <!-- =====================================================
       COOKIE CONSENT BANNER
       GA4: G-3R9SGKJGBQ
       ===================================================== -->
  <style>
    #cookie-banner {
      position: fixed;
      bottom: 24px;
      left: 50%;
      transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(120px);
      z-index: 99999;
      width: calc(100% - 32px);
      max-width: 680px;
      background: #1D3033;
      border-radius: 20px;
      padding: 20px 24px;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.35), 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 20px;
      opacity: 0;
      transition: transform 0.5s cubic-bezier(0.22,1,0.36,1), opacity 0.4s ease;
      pointer-events: none;
    }
    #cookie-banner.visible {
      transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(0);
      opacity: 1;
      pointer-events: auto;
    }
    #cookie-banner p { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75); font-size: 0.8125rem; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0; flex: 1; }
    #cookie-banner a { color: #B8914F; text-decoration: underline; }
    #cookie-banner a:hover { color: #A67A44; }
    .cookie-btn {
      border: none; border-radius: 12px; font-size: 0.8125rem; font-weight: 600;
      cursor: pointer; padding: 10px 20px; white-space: nowrap;
      transition: transform 0.2s cubic-bezier(0.22,1,0.36,1), opacity 0.2s;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }
    .cookie-btn:hover  { transform: translateY(-1px); opacity: 0.9; }
    .cookie-btn:active { transform: translateY(0); }
    #cookie-accept { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #A67A44, #B8914F); color: #fff; }
    #cookie-reject { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.15); color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2); }
    #cookie-customize { background: transparent; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5); padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12); font-weight: 400; font-size: 0.75rem; }
    @media (max-width: 540px) {
      #cookie-banner { flex-direction: column; align-items: stretch; gap: 12px; }
      .cookie-btn { text-align: center; }
    }
    #cookie-modal-overlay {
      position: fixed; inset: 0; z-index: 999999;
      background: rgba(0,0,0,0.55); backdrop-filter: blur(4px);
      display: flex; align-items: flex-end; justify-content: center;
      opacity: 0; pointer-events: none; transition: opacity 0.3s ease;
    }
    #cookie-modal-overlay.visible { opacity: 1; pointer-events: auto; }
    #cookie-modal {
      background: #fff; width: 100%; max-width: 520px;
      border-radius: 24px 24px 0 0; padding: 32px 28px 36px;
      transform: translateY(40px); transition: transform 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.22,1,0.36,1);
      max-height: 90vh; overflow-y: auto;
    }
    #cookie-modal-overlay.visible #cookie-modal { transform: translateY(0); }
    @media (min-width: 560px) {
      #cookie-modal-overlay { align-items: center; }
      #cookie-modal { border-radius: 24px; }
    }
    .cm-title { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 1.25rem; font-weight: 700; color: #1D3033; margin: 0 0 6px; }
    .cm-subtitle { font-size: 0.8125rem; color: #6b7280; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0 0 24px; }
    .cm-subtitle a { color: #A67A44; text-decoration: underline; }
    .cm-row { display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 16px; padding: 16px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #f3f4f6; }
    .cm-row:last-of-type { border-bottom: none; }
    .cm-row-text { flex: 1; }
    .cm-row-name { font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 600; color: #1D3033; margin: 0 0 3px; }
    .cm-row-desc { font-size: 0.78rem; color: #9ca3af; line-height: 1.55; margin: 0; }
    .cm-toggle { position: relative; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 2px; }
    .cm-toggle input { opacity: 0; width: 0; height: 0; position: absolute; }
    .cm-toggle-track { display: block; width: 44px; height: 24px; border-radius: 100px; background: #e5e7eb; cursor: pointer; transition: background 0.25s; position: relative; }
    .cm-toggle input:checked + .cm-toggle-track { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #A67A44, #B8914F); }
    .cm-toggle input:disabled + .cm-toggle-track { cursor: not-allowed; opacity: 0.6; }
    .cm-toggle-track::after { content: ''; position: absolute; top: 3px; left: 3px; width: 18px; height: 18px; border-radius: 50%; background: #fff; box-shadow: 0 1px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.18); transition: transform 0.25s cubic-bezier(0.22,1,0.36,1); }
    .cm-toggle input:checked + .cm-toggle-track::after { transform: translateX(20px); }
    .cm-actions { display: flex; gap: 10px; margin-top: 24px; }
    .cm-btn { flex: 1; border: none; border-radius: 12px; font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 600; padding: 12px 16px; cursor: pointer; transition: transform 0.2s cubic-bezier(0.22,1,0.36,1), opacity 0.2s; }
    .cm-btn:hover  { transform: translateY(-1px); opacity: 0.9; }
    .cm-btn:active { transform: translateY(0); }
    #cm-save { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #A67A44, #B8914F); color: #fff; }
    #cm-reject-all { background: #f3f4f6; color: #6b7280; }
  </style>

  <div id="cookie-banner" role="dialog" aria-label="Zgoda na pliki cookie">
    <p>Używamy plików cookie do celów statystycznych i marketingowych. Możesz wybrać, które akceptujesz. <a href="/privacy.html">Polityka prywatności</a></p>
    <button class="cookie-btn" id="cookie-customize">Personalizuj</button>
    <button class="cookie-btn" id="cookie-reject">Odrzuć wszystkie</button>
    <button class="cookie-btn" id="cookie-accept">Akceptuj wszystkie</button>
  </div>

  <div id="cookie-modal-overlay" role="dialog" aria-modal="true" aria-label="Ustawienia cookies">
    <div id="cookie-modal">
      <p class="cm-title">Ustawienia prywatności</p>
      <p class="cm-subtitle">Wybierz, które pliki cookie chcesz zaakceptować. <a href="/privacy.html">Polityka prywatności</a></p>
      <div class="cm-row">
        <div class="cm-row-text">
          <p class="cm-row-name">Niezbędne</p>
          <p class="cm-row-desc">Wymagane do działania strony (sesja, formularz). Nie można ich wyłączyć.</p>
        </div>
        <label class="cm-toggle"><input type="checkbox" checked disabled><span class="cm-toggle-track"></span></label>
      </div>
      <div class="cm-row">
        <div class="cm-row-text">
          <p class="cm-row-name">Statystyki</p>
          <p class="cm-row-desc">Google Analytics — mierzą ruch i zachowanie użytkowników. Dane są anonimizowane i nie identyfikują osobiście.</p>
        </div>
        <label class="cm-toggle"><input type="checkbox" id="toggle-statistics"><span class="cm-toggle-track"></span></label>
      </div>
      <div class="cm-row">
        <div class="cm-row-text">
          <p class="cm-row-name">Marketing</p>
          <p class="cm-row-desc">Google Ads / remarketing — pozwalają wyświetlać dopasowane reklamy. Twoje dane mogą być przekazywane partnerom reklamowym.</p>
        </div>
        <label class="cm-toggle"><input type="checkbox" id="toggle-marketing"><span class="cm-toggle-track"></span></label>
      </div>
      <div class="cm-actions">
        <button class="cm-btn" id="cm-reject-all">Odrzuć wszystkie</button>
        <button class="cm-btn" id="cm-save">Zapisz ustawienia</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <script is:inline>
    (function () {
      function saveConsent(statistics, marketing) {
        localStorage.setItem('cm_consent', JSON.stringify({ necessary: true, statistics: statistics, marketing: marketing, ts: Date.now(), version: '1.0' }));
      }
      function applyConsent(statistics, marketing) {
        gtag('consent', 'update', {
          analytics_storage:  statistics ? 'granted' : 'denied',
          ad_storage:         marketing  ? 'granted' : 'denied',
          ad_user_data:       marketing  ? 'granted' : 'denied',
          ad_personalization: marketing  ? 'granted' : 'denied'
        });
        if (statistics && typeof window.loadGA === 'function') { window.loadGA(); }
        if (!statistics || !marketing) {
          document.cookie.split(';').forEach(function (c) {
            var name = c.trim().split('=')[0];
            if (/^(_ga|_gid|_gat|_gcl|_gac)/.test(name)) {
              document.cookie = name + '=; expires=Thu, 01 Jan 1970 00:00:00 UTC; path=/; domain=' + location.hostname;
              document.cookie = name + '=; expires=Thu, 01 Jan 1970 00:00:00 UTC; path=/; domain=.' + location.hostname;
            }
          });
        }
      }
      function hideBanner() {
        var b = document.getElementById('cookie-banner');
        if (!b) return;
        b.style.opacity = '0';
        b.style.transform = 'translateX(-50%) translateY(120px)';
        setTimeout(function () { b.remove(); }, 500);
      }
      function closeModal() { document.getElementById('cookie-modal-overlay').classList.remove('visible'); }

      if (window._cmValid) {
        var d = window._cmData;
        if (d) {
          var togS = document.getElementById('toggle-statistics');
          var togM = document.getElementById('toggle-marketing');
          if (togS) togS.checked = !!d.statistics;
          if (togM) togM.checked = !!d.marketing;
        }
        return;
      }

      setTimeout(function () {
        var banner = document.getElementById('cookie-banner');
        if (banner) banner.classList.add('visible');
      }, 800);

      document.getElementById('cookie-accept').addEventListener('click', function () { saveConsent(true, true); applyConsent(true, true); hideBanner(); });
      document.getElementById('cookie-reject').addEventListener('click', function () { saveConsent(false, false); applyConsent(false, false); hideBanner(); });
      document.getElementById('cookie-customize').addEventListener('click', function () { document.getElementById('cookie-modal-overlay').classList.add('visible'); });
      document.getElementById('cookie-modal-overlay').addEventListener('click', function (e) { if (e.target === this) closeModal(); });
      document.getElementById('cm-save').addEventListener('click', function () {
        var s = document.getElementById('toggle-statistics').checked;
        var m = document.getElementById('toggle-marketing').checked;
        saveConsent(s, m); applyConsent(s, m); closeModal(); hideBanner();
      });
      document.getElementById('cm-reject-all').addEventListener('click', function () { saveConsent(false, false); applyConsent(false, false); closeModal(); hideBanner(); });
    })();
  </script>
</body>
</html>
